title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Maastricht Airport
description:
In this video we will have a look at Maastricht Airport which received an update on the scenery created by one of the community members. We will first look with the drone and after that look from the sky using an airplane.

If you would like to give the addon a try yourself visit the site below to download it:
https://flightsim.to/file/14431/ehbk-maastricht-airport
